{"tid":348602,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB證實腰斬《Big Boys歷險記》","createTime":"2017-08-05T23:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T13:55:52.000Z","uid":3806,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa40369d58120eab59effa1abd4627a0a7ccf89","tid":348602,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T23:45:44.000Z","msg":"TVB暑期特備節目《BigBoys歷險記》玩靈異題材，上周日播映奇門法科師傅「龍哥」在西貢的交通黑點超度，師傅念咒被指似Rap娛樂性十足，他「鬼上身」的一幕更震撼在網上瘋傳!今日傳出《BigBoys歷險記》遭腰斬消息，原本4集節目刪剪為2集，「龍哥」被消失。有網民留言罷睇，寫道:「畀番龍哥我呀!」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170805/20170805_e37079f54cf60906fa6c0MXGLiRCYfeJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170805%2F20170805_e37079f54cf60906fa6c0MXGLiRCYfeJ.jpg&h=bfe942d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8cf30004659ca91f8d0b89889f3804c99b603eb","tid":348602,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T23:53:18.000Z","msg":"屌牙"},{"pid":"cf7bb17c49ad86f75aa4f6fde5c1141593edee1a","tid":348602,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T00:00:38.000Z","msg":"瘋狂地rap"},{"pid":"2c4d65cd64993e14ebcecaac61dc63663fbab3a0","tid":348602,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T00:06:09.000Z","msg":"對tvb好失望"},{"pid":"0405cef79a19a5e6f997982300b2a80e8b5b2556","tid":348602,"uid":8572,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T00:19:17.000Z","msg":"三一一轉, 乾坤一開<br />\n玄天大帝指令一開, 七色令旗開哂佢<br />\n牛鬼蛇神, 是非小人走哂佢<br />\n清走, 一開, 關聖帝君指令, 一起<br />\n一接令旗, 一收, 兩收<br />\n三收, 四收, 五收, 六收<br />\n渣住哂佢, 乾坤一開, 通行無阻<br />\n乾坤一開<br />\n怨氣散走哂佢, 怨氣清走哂佢<br />\n乾坤一開, 心平氣和去投胎<br />\n乾坤一開, 不可帶一絲怨氣<br />\n一張白紙咁去投胎<br />\n怨氣清走哂佢, 乾坤一開<br />\n走得0既走, 清得0既清<br />\n散得0既散, 燒得0既燒<br />\n乾坤一開, 走哂佢. 走走走<br />\n一開, 一鬆, 乾坤一開<br />\n走走走..... 走!"},{"pid":"ed29154456d706d01ead61ae624081fe38225770","tid":348602,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0